metadata.name: Pixel Ape #1
metadata.description: **PUBLIC MINTING IS LIVE NOW: https://bapp.club.**  *Become a BAPP member for only .09 ETH.*  The BAPP is a set of 10,000 Bored Ape NFTs inspired by the original BAYC collection.  Each colorful, AI-pixelated NFT is a one-of-a-kind collectible that lives on the Ethereum blockchain.  Your Pixel Bored Ape also serves as your Club membership card, granting you access to exclusive benefits for Club members.
